@node "Version" "Version History"

 @{u}@{fg shine}Version History@{uu}@{fg text}:

 @{u}v1.0 (6.APR.97)@{uu}
 - Original public release.

 @{u}v1.1 (7.APR.97)@{uu}
 - Corrected a few minor problems in the commodity as
   well as added the sample config file to the distribution
   archive which was forgotten. Fixed a problem with the
   prefs program not not being able to load the prefs file
   and. Please keep in mind that in order for you to update
   the prefs, this commodity MUST be the last to be loaded,
   otherwise some of the vectors that are patched may be
   patched by some other program and WinSound will not be
   able to remove the old and set the new sounds for the
   changed vectors.

 @{u}v1.2 (7.APR.97)@{uu}
 Corrected Typeo in Installer Script.

 @{u}V1.3 (25.JUN.97)@{uu}
 - corrected bug in commodity not replying to a message
   sent by the prefs program
 - slimlined code for datatype triggering
 - added support for WindowToBack, WindowToFront, ZipWindow,
   SizeWindow.
 - compiled processor specific versions

 @{u}V1.4beta (12.10.97)@{uu}
 - corrected bug that would not Permit() if something failed
 - properly disposed of datatype objects before recreating
 - rewrote the prefs program using SAS/C and GadTools. Now
   supports complete keyboard control.
 - added ScreenToFront, ScreenToBack, OpenScreen, Closescreen
   functions
 - new config file format which handles paths properly now
 - the commodity now spawns the prefs via CreateNewProc() as
   it should have to begin with instead of Execute()
 - updated documentation.
@endnode

